{"tid":2220404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新界校長會安排100名跨境學童於深圳考呈分試","createTime":"2020-09-27T15:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T15:39:20.000Z","uid":210495,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"beced55a3edcf1d9dc2b76f5407f1b567662f175","tid":2220404,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"新界校長會副主席朱偉林表示，身在內地的跨境學童於深圳福田一間學校應考，由內地教師在場監考，本港教師經視像監考，考生應考前要量體溫及出示「健康碼」，完成考試後，試卷會經電腦掃瞄及速遞傳送返港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551928-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551928-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=80ca31b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551928-20200927.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=75793042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551928-20200927.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1551928_1_20200927214448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1551928_1_20200927214448.jpg&h=9ec01ec9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}